-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-31/sage-group-pulls-out-of-bain-capital-s-auction-of-teamsystem-ft-reports.html

          
          
             Sage Group Plc  pulled out from the
600 million-euro ($783 million) TeamSystem SpA auction, leaving
Cinven Ltd. and HgCapital as the only bidders, the Financial
Times  reported , citing an unidentified person close to Sage.  
 TeamSystem is being sold by Bain Capital LLC, the newspaper
said. The bidding price may drop after Sageâ€™s exit, according to
the FT.  
